or.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/sina-frei-specialized-s-works-epic-xco-world-champs-bike-check-mirror-saddle-3d-printed-carbon-rails-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/sina-frei-specialized-s-works-epic-xco-world-champs-bike-check-mirror-saddle-3d-printed-carbon-rails-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/sina-frei-specialized-s-works-epic-xco-world-champs-bike-check-mirror-saddle-3d-printed-carbon-rails-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/sina-frei-specialized-s-works-epic-xco-world-champs-bike-check-mirror-saddle-3d-printed-carbon-rails-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/sina-frei-specialized-s-works-epic-xco-world-champs-bike-check-mirror-saddle-3d-printed-carbon-rails.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/sina-frei-specialized-s-works-epic-xco-world-champs-bike-check-ht-pedals.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/sina-frei-specialized-s-works-epic-xco-world-champs-bike-check-ht-pedals-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"sina frei 2023 scotland world champs bike oil slick ht leopard pedals\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/sina-frei-specialized-s-works-epic-xco-world-champs-bike-check-ht-pedals-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/sina-frei-specialized-s-works-epic-xco-world-champs-bike-check-ht-pedals-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/sina-frei-specialized-s-works-epic-xco-world-champs-bike-check-ht-pedals-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/sina-frei-specialized-s-works-epic-xco-world-champs-bike-check-ht-pedals-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/sina-frei-specialized-s-works-epic-xco-world-champs-bike-check-ht-pedals-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/sina-frei-specialized-s-works-epic-xco-world-champs-bike-check-ht-pedals-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/sina-frei-specialized-s-works-epic-xco-world-champs-bike-check-ht-pedals.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Aside from the RockShox Flight Attendant suspension, the oil slick-finished HT Leopard pedals and <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/specialized-3d-printed-power-pro-mirror-saddle-review/\" target=\"_blank\">Specialized Power Pro Mirror</a> 3D-printed saddle, and the Syntace stem, Sina’s Specialized Epic EVO XC bike for the 2023 UCI Cycling World Champs is of stock configuration.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Good luck to Sina and the rest of the <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/specialized_factoryracing/\" target=\"_blank\">Specialized Factory Racing</a> team this weekend!</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.specialized.com/\" target=\"_blank\">specialized.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/sina-frei-specialized-epic-flight-attendant/\">Pro Bike Check: Sina Frei’s Specialized Epic EVO with Flight Attendant</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Jessie-May Morgan","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"7b6eaaa3bdca21e50ce57d9b6e1e7b33d8fc57b61436b3611b6823ff05ca712d","category":"Cycling"}